snippet.title: One Troll Army Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Defend your fort from nasty invaders in One Troll Army. 

Want to help make the game free? Join us Thursday 19th May from 9am CEST. If Twitch Chat beats us, the game will be free - http://twitch.tv/tinybuild

Steam - http://store.steampowered.com/app/438680
